content.text:
I'm ready to help you with the SPLICE project. I can see this is a video editing enhancement platform with AI-powered music generation, consisting of a backend API, Adobe plugins (CEP and UXP), and a Next.js frontend.

The backend is currently deployed to Railway at `https://splice-api-production.up.railway.app`, and I can see there are many modified files in your working directory along with numerous documentation and research files.

What would you like me to help you with today? I can assist with:

- Development tasks (features, bug fixes, testing)
- Deployment and infrastructure
- Code review and troubleshooting
- Documentation updates
- Any other aspect of the SPLICE project

Just let me know what you need, and I'll get started.
